Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.13,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.34,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.14,0:00:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.42,0:01:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.53,0:01:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.95,0:01:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac175年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的領導人被暗殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部鋼彈被派往地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本應是為了報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但由於OZ在宇宙的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非擺出支配的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是處處以協調為先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是，衛星接受OZ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在支配地球和宇宙的進程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.61,0:01:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈被視作\N叛徒的象徵給孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無家可歸的鋼彈及其駕駛員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不斷轉變的時代裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.32,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以存在意義為賭注繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…宇宙服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙服是攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快制止它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,障礙…要清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十話\N潛入月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大量鋼彈特殊合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被運進月面基地的工場裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是為了製造新型機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過最近的連續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連我的身體也支持不了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你不能說得婉轉一點的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你代替我上學就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用你的名字辦理入學手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?這玩笑真過份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字在這裡\N多引人注目也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就乖乖地等待身體痊癒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使叫他別勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙也一定不會聽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去到月球後才決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搶奪，還是破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重力是地球的六分之一的月球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的居住空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不適合的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙衛星的完成期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類在月球進行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.79,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各種研究設施\N和巨大工場的建設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.26,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來，月球更發展為\N宇宙觀光地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招待由地球來的遊客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聯合的壓迫前相當繁榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於OZ成功把聯合軍解體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球被準許繼續作為觀光地經營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事被人們當作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙恢復和平的預兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星間的移動也變得自由了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的OZ看來在盡力誘惑宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了討好衛星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ要用盡各種懷柔手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦令他們信任之後就簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資源和勞動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會在一瞬間被OZ吸乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少要造出些難馴的悍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令OZ為難吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[麥丘留士]的防禦系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[拜葉特]的主體組合後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大致就成形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成只是時間的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠照OZ的吩咐工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然事情已經交由蕾蒂‧安負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來會從衛星市民裡挑選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛這兩部機動戰士的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會有趣起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何，不會那麼順利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛不會採取\N那麼轉折的方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那個人會更加直接了當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，我們完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ追求的強力機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.36,0:05:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後証明它們也能消滅OZ啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.61,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ說想在宇宙建立國家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從聯合的支配體制解放出來後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民間性也好，衛星之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球的交流也重新開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這的確是OZ的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但無必要連衛星今後的行政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也聽從OZ的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.56,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，從現在衛星的規模來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信不作為一個國家會更奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，但問題就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要工業由軍事技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和機動戰士的生產組成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，衛星代表團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然對那文件有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看過聯合胡亂使用\N軍備後的他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會認為機動戰士的生產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等同死亡商人的行為吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.82,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支援OZ的國家想要宇宙的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了用作軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為主張和平\N的衛星不會接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.93,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在被認為是制衡力就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那段期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙裡不夠的東西\N也會齊備了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙裡不夠的東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確的秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.45,0:07:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，要你們久等，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位已經看過手上的文件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.59,0:07:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有宇宙衛星\N被地球認為是威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因相信也在於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的非主流組織裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.46,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為建立國家\N是有意義的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，對主要工業有問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.61,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在需要軍備\N作為制衡力的想法下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界不可能得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們從過去的歷史裡學到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星有可能確立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球分開的新秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技術力成為瑰寶\N令我們非常自豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不可以想及生產軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.06,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在我心裡，戰爭已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ是軍事組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們努力平息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球上重覆著的紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某段時期，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經像各位一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以不尋求軍事力量\N的和平為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.25,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，那裡誕生了甚麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不須要胡亂戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，失去戰鬥姿態的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能道出人類的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被男人的那種姿態迷住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到OZ把它復原至這地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不可以把鋼彈交給OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那問題我想問妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深夜潛入來裝炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不是等閒之輩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先把那個引爆器交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經有必死之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會交出鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種爆炸下毫無損傷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能由衷地高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不愧是鋼彈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!真胡來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被OZ發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那個女人幫了我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們死也要奪回\N卡特爾少爺的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里歐部隊出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在鋼彈04的機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易潛入來卻弄成這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞布度的作戰沒好結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?你說了甚麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點帶卡特爾少爺的鋼彈來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做甚麼? 奧達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!離遠一點戰鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好不容易才搶到這部運輸機啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們原定OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會幫我們把鋼彈修復完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想不到這麼快就行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞夫馬特!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.97,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!很完美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功逃脫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼?為何停下來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止無謂的戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!是那個女人的聲音!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!是奧達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果是我認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這情形，他會破壞鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認識的人覺得破壞是悲哀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想設法修好它\N令他高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也是鋼彈的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是中東的馬格亞那隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這部鋼彈交給我們處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子看來也是好孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的朋友也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去把另一個好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟下的東西撿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是衛星為了自衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.37,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日在宇宙進行的有意義影象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被挑選出來的年輕志願兵們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將會肩負宇宙的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何所有人都照OZ的說話做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕人們在假設為實戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射擊測試裡取得好成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，在全體的前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備了多個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設為敵人的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手是模擬彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但被擊中會有很強的衝擊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.70,0:12:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!迎擊開始!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終只是新人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.10,0:13:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?\N那傢伙…是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是一號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演習完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.34,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一號機駕駛員，核對名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛者，特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，特洛瓦‧巴頓有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行過多少次模擬也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒理由能在初次實戰裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出那種迴避動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.03,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在某處受過訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是相當高度的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,履歷已經完全檢查過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，那是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，他有潛在的天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以來無用武之地的天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他有可能是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派來破壞OZ的特工…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，馬上查明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追加演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把下一個目標完全毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼?特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!他果然是鋼彈的駕駛員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那支雷射砲借給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是鋼彈特殊合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以里歐的來福槍不會有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,產生地球和衛星的誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑起戰亂的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在即將被祈求和平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星市民親手毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，請靜心欣賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.31,0:14:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，死神，不要輕易被毀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次演習，開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腦波和心跳也完全無變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是完美的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，還有若干疑問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他擁有參加OZ的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有天份的人會了解OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…眼淚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型的機動戰士嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,設計中的零件還很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一號機練習生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校要見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在那裡等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校，很危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還有可能是鋼彈的駕駛員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我獨自和他見面看來比較好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來是想了解OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不見他是沒禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同是愛護宇宙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交談起來也會起勁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥爾特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何害怕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥快要結束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.65,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸會，我叫蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人就是蕾蒂‧安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ宇宙軍最高指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安上級特校嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你曾經以工程用機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修補衛星的外壁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在演習的成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令OZ的現役士兵很驚奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.10,0:17:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為我有天份作為士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我被錄用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起令宇宙和平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想自己的本領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.68,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能為打倒聯合宇宙軍效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒想過宇宙的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.32,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我認為我是適合OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,適合OZ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡一面擺出友好姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面想支配宇宙的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們會評為卑鄙的手段吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配?卑鄙的手段?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙小人被認同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.32,0:18:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校妳去冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，特校，這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校被騙，我也不會被騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校命令你兩小時後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.67,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行OZ新型機動戰士的測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但特校她現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿起軍服的\N蕾蒂‧安特校很堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.38,0:18:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她或許不會放過可疑的你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是特列斯大人的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徵召得比想像中快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這五人是從衛星市民裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,選拔出來的駕駛員候補生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中，特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是最優秀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他能駕御任何機動戰士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.76,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩部機動戰士\N不能輕易操縱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來造得比鋼彈好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥丘留士80%，拜葉特50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何須要開發不同的類型?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩部機是\N基於戰鬥的基本姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進攻和防守達至極限時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有何結果而製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特有一支能源砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的體積會盡量保留機動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥丘留士有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵擋那支能源砲的防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩部機戰鬥會有何結果?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是優秀駕駛員駕駛的取勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士的性能競爭是無聊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.04,0:20:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以駕駛者的能力來決定勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ推薦的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好聰明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦特士，你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，是他將要駕駛的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我批準發問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，今日會展示甚麼測試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥丘留士的防禦方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是能造出電場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.36,0:20:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵擋敵人能源的革新系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特方面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特還未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未注入能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?拜葉特動了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開動麥丘留士的防護罩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.33,0:22:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?我的兵器優秀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他來取我們的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.93,0:22:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.93,0:22:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.93,0:22:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.43,0:22:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.93,0:23:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.43,0:23:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.93,0:23:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.36,0:23:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有部白色機動戰士接近衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當查明那是傑克斯駕駛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.70,0:23:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安命令特洛瓦和希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.47,0:23:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展開攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.74,0:23:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，受了傷的卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.70,0:23:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到親切的溫拿家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他爸爸在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.51,0:23:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自承擔人們的責難和咒罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.41,0:23:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第二十一話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.88,0:23:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲傷的卡特爾

